title: Grateful Dead Live at Des Moines State Fair Grandstand on 1974-06-16
description:
Set 1

Bertha, Mexicali Blues, Row Jimmy, Beat It On Down The Line, Scarlet Begonias, Black Throated Wind, Sugaree, El Paso, It Must Have Been The Roses, Jack Straw, China Cat Sunflower> I Know You Rider, Around & Around

Set 2

U.S. Blues, The Race is On, Eyes Of The World-> Big River, Playin' In The Band, Tennessee Jed, Me & My Uncle, Deal, Greatest Story Ever Told, Ship Of Fools

Set 3

Truckin'-> Nobody's Fault But Mine-> Wharf Rat-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad, E: Casey Jones

Setlist order not 100% certain. The list here is given in the order of a ~1999-circulated SBD.

reviews.review_text: how can i possibly be the first to review this show... mid-term long-time archive-ist. listen to hundreds of shows off here. my first review. nothing specific. just a huge set list from an incredible period. see if you like it.
Des Moines 74' This is typical june 74' which means its absolutely perfect.
